## 3 Design Goals

- âœ… Composable â€” each transformation behaves like a unary function of the previous result.
- âœ… Deferred â€” no execution until .run() is called.
- âœ… Async-safe â€” promises and async functions are first-class citizens.
- âœ… Stateless â€” no global mutation; every pipeline owns its own context.
- âœ… Ergonomic â€” visually aligns with the future |> operator.

